    <div class="example--right">
      <p class="example--body">Every Carbon.io Service is capable of generating its own docs. You can currently choose between Github-flavored Markdown or static HTML using Aglio. The docs here are auto generated from <a href="https://github.com/carbon-io-guides/example__contact-service">our official tutorial</a>.</p>
      
